# BidPazar Full-Stack Project Brief

## Core Tech Stack
- Next.js 15.2+
- React 19+
- TypeScript
- TailwindCSS
- Prisma
- PostgreSQL
- Socket.io
- MediaSoup

## Key Components
- User authentication and account management
- Product marketplace browsing
- Live auction streaming and participation
- Real-time bidding interface
- Live chat during streams
- Private messaging between users
- Admin dashboard
- Payment processing
- Database management
- WebSocket server
- WebRTC streaming server

## Full-Stack Architecture
- Next.js App Router for routing and API routes
- React components with TypeScript
- TailwindCSS for styling
- React Hook Form for form management
- Zod for validation
- Prisma for database operations
- Socket.io for real-time updates
- MediaSoup for WebRTC streaming
- Server-side rendering and API routes

## Pages/Routes
- Home/landing
- Authentication (sign-in, sign-up)
- Product listings and details
- Live stream browser and viewer
- Dashboard for users
- Admin panel
- Messaging interface
- Static pages (About, Terms, FAQ)
- API routes for all backend operations

## Integration Points
- Database operations with Prisma
- WebSocket server for real-time updates
- WebRTC streaming with MediaSoup
- Payment processing
- Notifications system
- Authentication system
- File storage
- Email/SMS services